1
00:00:23,893 --> 00:00:25,286
Ah, solo es Ashru.

2
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:28,080
Entonces... ¿todo bien?

3
00:00:43,340 --> 00:00:44,786
Normalmente

4
00:00:44,826 --> 00:00:47,650
